We may send users periodic emails containing information about the website, administrative notices about a user’s account, updates on new service features, usage tips relating to the services and user satisfaction questions. <br/>
We may access user information for one of the following administrative purposes: <br/>
1. To examine system accounting logs and other company records to resolve email and other system errors or problems. <br/>
2. For billing purposes. <br/>
